SOURCE: https://github.com/shopify/polaris/blob/main/documentation/guides/migrating-from-v3-to-v4.md#2025-04-22_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: HTML
CODE:
```
<!-- old -->
<link
  rel="stylesheet"
  href="https://sdks.shopifycdn.com/polaris/3.21.1/polaris.min.css"
/>

<!-- new -->
<link
  rel="stylesheet"
  href="https://unpkg.com/@shopify/polaris@4.0.0/styles.min.css"
/>
```

